description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Cooter purrs with a rating of 95, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 190, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Leverage for East, 8 for South, and 5 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90952-36852-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [190 Votes, Hall of Fame]
